764  public virtual bool PreProcessWmChar(ref Message m)
765  {
766  if (ModifierKeys == Keys.Control)
767  {
768  return _hexBox.BasePreProcessMessage(ref m);
769  }
770 
771  bool sw = _hexBox._byteProvider.SupportsWriteByte();
772  bool si = _hexBox._byteProvider.SupportsInsertBytes();
773  bool sd = _hexBox._byteProvider.SupportsDeleteBytes();
774 
775  long pos = _hexBox._bytePos;
776  long sel = _hexBox._selectionLength;
777  int cp = _hexBox._byteCharacterPos;
778 
779  if (
780  !sw && pos != _hexBox._byteProvider.Length ||
781  !si && pos == _hexBox._byteProvider.Length)
782  {
783  return _hexBox.BasePreProcessMessage(ref m);
784  }
785 
786  char c = (char) m.WParam.ToInt32();
787 
788  if (Uri.IsHexDigit(c))
789  {
790  if (RaiseKeyPress(c))
791  {
792  return true;
793  }
794 
795  if (_hexBox.ReadOnly)
796  {
797  return true;
798  }
799 
800  bool isInsertMode = pos == _hexBox._byteProvider.Length;
801 
802  // do insert when insertActive = true
803  if (!isInsertMode && si && _hexBox.InsertActive && cp == 0)
804  {
805  isInsertMode = true;
806  }
807 
808  if (sd && si && sel > 0)
809  {
810  _hexBox._byteProvider.DeleteBytes(pos, sel);
811  isInsertMode = true;
812  cp = 0;
813  _hexBox.SetPosition(pos, cp);
814  }
815 
816  _hexBox.ReleaseSelection();
817 
818  byte currentByte;
819  if (isInsertMode)
820  {
821  currentByte = 0;
822  }
823  else
824  {
825  currentByte = _hexBox._byteProvider.ReadByte(pos);
826  }
827 
828  string sCb = currentByte.ToString("X", System.Threading.Thread.CurrentThread.CurrentCulture);
829  if (sCb.Length == 1)
830  {
831  sCb = "0" + sCb;
832  }
833 
834  string sNewCb = c.ToString();
835  if (cp == 0)
836  {
837  sNewCb += sCb.Substring(1, 1);
838  }
839  else
840  {
841  sNewCb = sCb.Substring(0, 1) + sNewCb;
842  }
843 
844  byte newcb = byte.Parse(sNewCb, NumberStyles.AllowHexSpecifier,
845  System.Threading.Thread.CurrentThread.CurrentCulture);
846 
847  if (isInsertMode)
848  {
849  _hexBox._byteProvider.InsertBytes(pos, new byte[] {newcb});
850  }
851  else
852  {
853  _hexBox._byteProvider.WriteByte(pos, newcb);
854  }
855 
856  PerformPosMoveRight();
857 
858  _hexBox.Invalidate();
859  return true;
860  }
861  else
862  {
863  return _hexBox.BasePreProcessMessage(ref m);
864  }
865  }

878  public virtual bool PreProcessWmKeyUp(ref Message m)
879  {
880  Keys vc = (Keys) m.WParam.ToInt32();
881 
882  Keys keyData = vc | ModifierKeys;
883 
884  switch (keyData)
885  {
886  case Keys.ShiftKey:
887  case Keys.Insert:
888  if (RaiseKeyUp(keyData))
889  {
890  return true;
891  }
892 
893  break;
894  }
895 
896  switch (keyData)
897  {
898  case Keys.ShiftKey:
899  _shiftDown = false;
900  return true;
901  case Keys.Insert:
902  return PreProcessWmKeyUp_Insert(ref m);
903  default:
904  return _hexBox.BasePreProcessMessage(ref m);
905  }
906  }

909  {
910  _hexBox.InsertActive = !_hexBox.InsertActive;
911  return true;
912  }

925  private Dictionary<Keys, MessageDelegate> MessageHandlers
926  {
927  get
928  {
929  if (_messageHandlers == null)
930  {
931  _messageHandlers = new Dictionary<Keys, MessageDelegate>
932  {
933  {Keys.Left, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_Left)}, // move left
934  {Keys.Up, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_Up)}, // move up
935  {Keys.Right, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_Right)}, // move right
936  {Keys.Down, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_Down)}, // move down
937  {Keys.PageUp, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_PageUp)}, // move pageup
938  {Keys.PageDown, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_PageDown)}, // move page down
939  {
940  Keys.Left | Keys.Shift, new MessageDelegate(PreProcessWmKeyDown_ShiftLeft)
941  }, // move left with selection

969  protected virtual bool PerformPosMoveLeft()
970  {

972  long sel = _hexBox._selectionLength;

984  {
985  return true;
986  }

991  }

1144  public override bool PreProcessWmKeyDown(ref Message m)
1145  {

1166  case Keys.Tab:

1187  public override bool PreProcessWmChar(ref Message m)
1188  {
1189  if (ModifierKeys == Keys.Control)
1190  {
1191  return _hexBox.BasePreProcessMessage(ref m);
1192  }
1193 
1194  bool sw = _hexBox._byteProvider.SupportsWriteByte();
1195  bool si = _hexBox._byteProvider.SupportsInsertBytes();
1196  bool sd = _hexBox._byteProvider.SupportsDeleteBytes();
1197 
1198  long pos = _hexBox._bytePos;
1199  long sel = _hexBox._selectionLength;
1200  int cp = _hexBox._byteCharacterPos;
1201 
1202  if (
1203  !sw && pos != _hexBox._byteProvider.Length ||
1204  !si && pos == _hexBox._byteProvider.Length)
1205  {
1206  return _hexBox.BasePreProcessMessage(ref m);
1207  }
1208 
1209  char c = (char) m.WParam.ToInt32();
1210 
1211  if (RaiseKeyPress(c))
1212  {
1213  return true;
1214  }
1215 
1216  if (_hexBox.ReadOnly)
1217  {
1218  return true;
1219  }
1220 
1221  bool isInsertMode = pos == _hexBox._byteProvider.Length;
1222 
1223  // do insert when insertActive = true
1224  if (!isInsertMode && si && _hexBox.InsertActive)
1225  {
1226  isInsertMode = true;
1227  }
1228 
1229  if (sd && si && sel > 0)
1230  {
1231  _hexBox._byteProvider.DeleteBytes(pos, sel);
1232  isInsertMode = true;
1233  cp = 0;
1234  _hexBox.SetPosition(pos, cp);
1235  }
1236 
1237  _hexBox.ReleaseSelection();
1238 
1239  byte b = _hexBox.ByteCharConverter.ToByte(c);
1240  if (isInsertMode)
1241  {
1242  _hexBox._byteProvider.InsertBytes(pos, new byte[] {b});
1243  }
1244  else
1245  {
1246  _hexBox._byteProvider.WriteByte(pos, b);
1247  }
1248 
1249  PerformPosMoveRightByte();
1250  _hexBox.Invalidate();
1251 
1252  return true;
1253  }

1625  private void vScrollBar_Scroll(object sender, ScrollEventArgs e)
1626  {
1627  switch (e.Type)
1628  {
1629  case ScrollEventType.Last:
1630  break;
1631  case ScrollEventType.EndScroll:
1632  break;
1633  case ScrollEventType.SmallIncrement:
1634  PerformScrollLineDown();
1635  break;
1636  case ScrollEventType.SmallDecrement:
1637  PerformScrollLineUp();
1638  break;
1639  case ScrollEventType.LargeIncrement:
1640  PerformScrollPageDown();
1641  break;
1642  case ScrollEventType.LargeDecrement:
1643  PerformScrollPageUp();
1644  break;
1645  case ScrollEventType.ThumbPosition:
1646  long lPos = FromScrollPos(e.NewValue);
1647  PerformScrollThumpPosition(lPos);
1648  break;
1649  case ScrollEventType.ThumbTrack:
1650  // to avoid performance problems use a refresh delay implemented with a timer
1651  if (_thumbTrackTimer.Enabled) // stop old timer
1652  {
1653  _thumbTrackTimer.Enabled = false;
1654  }
1655 
1656  // perform scroll immediately only if last refresh is very old
1657  int currentThumbTrack = Environment.TickCount;
1658  if (currentThumbTrack - _lastThumbtrack > THUMPTRACKDELAY)
1659  {
1660  PerformScrollThumbTrack(null, null);
1661  _lastThumbtrack = currentThumbTrack;
1662  break;
1663  }
1664 
1665  // start thumbtrack timer
1666  _thumbTrackPosition = FromScrollPos(e.NewValue);
1667  _thumbTrackTimer.Enabled = true;
1668  break;
1669  case ScrollEventType.First:
1670  break;
1671  default:
1672  break;
1673  }
1674 
1675  e.NewValue = ToScrollPos(_scrollVpos);
1676  }
1677 
1681  private void PerformScrollThumbTrack(object sender, EventArgs e)
1682  {
1683  _thumbTrackTimer.Enabled = false;
1684  PerformScrollThumpPosition(_thumbTrackPosition);
1685  _lastThumbtrack = Environment.TickCount;
1686  }

1688  private void UpdateScrollSize()
1689  {
1690  // calc scroll bar info
1691  if (VScrollBarVisible && _byteProvider != null && _byteProvider.Length > 0 && _iHexMaxHBytes != 0)
1692  {
1693  long scrollmax =
1694  (long) Math.Ceiling((_byteProvider.Length + 1) / (double) _iHexMaxHBytes - _iHexMaxVBytes);
1695  scrollmax = Math.Max(0, scrollmax);
1696 
1697  long scrollpos = _startByte / _iHexMaxHBytes;
1698 
1699  if (scrollmax < _scrollVmax)
1700  {
1701  /* Data size has been decreased. */
1702  if (_scrollVpos == _scrollVmax)
1703  {
1704  /* Scroll one line up if we at bottom. */
1705  PerformScrollLineUp();
1706  }
1707  }
1708 
1709  if (scrollmax == _scrollVmax && scrollpos == _scrollVpos)
1710  {
1711  return;
1712  }
1713 
1714  _scrollVmin = 0;
1715  _scrollVmax = scrollmax;
1716  _scrollVpos = Math.Min(scrollpos, scrollmax);
1717  UpdateVScroll();
1718  }
1719  else if (VScrollBarVisible)
1720  {
1721  // disable scroll bar
1722  _scrollVmin = 0;
1723  _scrollVmax = 0;
1724  _scrollVpos = 0;
1725  UpdateVScroll();
1726  }
1727  }

1746  private int ToScrollPos(long value)
1747  {
1748  int max = 65535;
1749 
1750  if (_scrollVmax < max)
1751  {
1752  return (int) value;
1753  }
1754  else
1755  {
1756  double valperc = value / (double) _scrollVmax * 100;
1757  int res = (int) Math.Floor(max / (double) 100 * valperc);
1758  res = (int) Math.Max(_scrollVmin, res);
1759  res = (int) Math.Min(_scrollVmax, res);
1760  return res;
1761  }
1762  }

1764  private long FromScrollPos(int value)
1765  {
1766  int max = 65535;
1767  if (_scrollVmax < max)
1768  {
1769  return value;
1770  }
1771  else
1772  {
1773  double valperc = value / (double) max * 100;
1774  long res = (int) Math.Floor(_scrollVmax / (double) 100 * valperc);
1775  return res;
1776  }
1777  }

4993  private byte[] ConvertHexToBytes(string hex)

5000  hex = hex.Trim();
